    <sys:String x:Key="MousePerformance.Status.Paused.Hint">点击“采集”可继续追加，点击“重置”可清空当前记录。</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="MousePerformance.Status.NoDevice.Pill">未检测到设备</sys:String>
