    <sys:String x:Key="MousePerformance.Status.DeviceDisconnected.Hint">重新选择设备并点击“采集”，将开始新会话。</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="MousePerformance.Chart.WindowTitle">鼠标性能图表</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="MousePerformance.Chart.WindowHint">拖拽可平移；滚轮会优先缩放横轴，达到 1 ms/格后再缩放纵轴；按住 Shift 并滚轮可仅缩放横轴；按住 Ctrl 并滚轮可仅缩放纵轴；按住 Shift+Ctrl 并滚轮可同步缩放横轴与纵轴；双击可重置视图。</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="MousePerformance.Chart.Action.SavePng">保存 PNG</sys:String>
